<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">How We Protect Personal Information.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We maintain appropriate administrative, technical, and physical safeguards designed to protect the personal information you provide against accidental, unlawful, or unauthorized destruction, loss, alteration, access, disclosure, or use. That said, it is not possible to guarantee the security of information transmitted online, and you assume some risk with regard to the security of information you provide through any website, including this Site.</span></p>
